FBIS4-43630 "drweu118_o_94001" FBIS-WEU-94-118 Daily Report 17 Jun 1994 CYPRUS Foreign Minister Returns From UN, Washington, London Foreign Minister Returns From UN, Washington, London NC1706213094 Nicosia Cyprus Broadcasting Corporation Radio Network in Greek 2100 GMT 17 Jun 94 NC1706213094 Nicosia Cyprus Broadcasting Corporation Radio Network Greek BFN [Excerpt] Foreign Minister Alekos Mikhailidhis returned a short while ago from visits to the United Nations, Washington, and London where he discussed the situation unfolding in the Cyprus issue following the latest report by UN Secretary General Butrus Butrus- Ghali and the new contacts between the UN and [Turkish Cypriot Leader] Rauf Denktas. Foreign Minister Mikhailidhis presented a document to the UN secretary general in which the Cyprus Government calls on the permanent members of the UN Security Council to hold deliberations for a new beginning in the Cyprus issue through the investigation of new options. [passage omitted]
